    "description": {
      "value": "<section class=\"secret\">\n<p>The {creature} fixes its gaze on one creature it can see within 10 feet of it. The target must succeed on a  <strong>DC 18 Wisdom</strong> saving throw against this magic or become grappled for 1 minute. The grappled target can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. If a target's saving throw is successful or the effect ends for it, the target is immune to the {creature}'s gaze for the next 24 hours.</p>\n</section>\n<p>The {creature} fixes its gaze on one creature it can see within 10 feet of it. The target must make a <strong>Wisdom</strong> saving throw.</p>",
